Daemos arrived at Zardus' location outside the Iron Fist (I think that's 
where he is) and gave him a datadisk.

Daemos:
These are the profiles of Belthassan, Melchana and Gesper, the three 
tripredacus that just arrived on planet. It has been a long time since I saw 
them, so these may not not be fully up to date. As for now, I will go to the 
Igl. If anybody needs a ride, come aboard!!

He entered the Hellgate and started the engines, waiting for any volunteer 
to come aboard.
